::Feline::

She watched as Skuletron tried to make Zardus laugh.  He had better 
not try any of that mind stuff on me, she thought.  She had to smile 
though, it would be nice to see Zardus smile for once.  

She walked over to the dispencer and got herself a drink.  She got 
two more for the Zardus and Skulletron.  She took the drinks to the 
table and sat down waiting to see if Zardus would smile.
